{"tid":2422740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年第四季向英國尋求政治庇護數字大降50%","createTime":"2021-02-25T11:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T13:26:23.000Z","uid":27530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8b26405f0d67d891022666ba00fe9765c4e20dbf","tid":2422740,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ov4fee0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fov4fee0.jpg&h=9e5f25fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據英國內政部的統計數字，2020年第四季共有21人向英國尋求政治庇護，比同年第三季大降約50%，當中19人為主要申請者，2人為申請者家眷；8人抵達英國機場口岸後申請庇護，13人則在入境英國後申請。至於性別及年齡方面，尋求庇護者中分別有13男8女，3人為18歲以下人士、18至29歲16人、50至69歲2人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/J6BC3FVSVJE6LCPHRVFK7WZ2FQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FJ6BC3FVSVJE6LCPHRVFK7WZ2FQ%2F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=f65e7677\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FJ6BC3FVSVJE6LCPHRVFK7WZ2FQ%2F&h=b9274a77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/J6BC3FVSVJE6LCPHRVFK7WZ2FQ/</a>"},{"pid":"13cff91f03dc079054e1c14655bb46737990c384","tid":2422740,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91684028c299aaabaaa131669ce075ae2c45dbe","tid":2422740,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1545ff63fd1ebbf27068066b429a11bcab294c8","tid":2422740,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:24:32.000Z","msg":"正常都少左，因為英國直接開左 LOTR 救人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d人轉左去 apply LOTR"},{"pid":"bf28b0b730af12b13bbc07351409924